title: Hour 3 - Which HR Number Is Aaron Judge Chasing?, Marcus Smart
itunes:title: Hour 3 - Which HR Number Is Aaron Judge Chasing?, Marcus Smart
description:
Dan and the Danettes debate which single season HR record New York Yankees slugger Aaron Judge is actually chasing. And he talks to Boston Celtic G and Defensive Player of the Year, Marcus Smart about the rumors he may be traded for Kevin Durant.
